      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，客户端用子图Cliente包含C1到C4。C1和C3都是CloudNative_HelmChart对吧？C2是K8sCluster，C4是ServiceMesh。中间层Vite只有一个P1也是HelmChart？",
