      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Vite层就P1一个HelmChart作为编排入口。服务端Servidor要复杂一些，需要五个组件：S1和S3是DockerImage，S2和S4是Serverless，S5是HelmChart做最终交付。",
